{"tid":2292491,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣F16失蹤機師變節去左廈門？！","createTime":"2020-11-19T13:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T05:23:09.000Z","uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b47f91e2050b336602a3008695c103c28399004c","tid":2292491,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnbCKdj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnbCKdj.jpg&h=1bbb3cc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dr1K8E1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdr1K8E1.jpg&h=c6c44e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7SAoEMH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7SAoEMH.jpg&h=ea39699e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11755d224c5cb007bd86be28e94cd94f53ef98ef","tid":2292491,"uid":217416,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"戰機Foodpanda<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68f42c729d39f37a73bdba057dcf21f46bc3512","tid":2292491,"uid":210755,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11755d224c5cb007bd86be28e94cd94f53ef98ef","tid":2292491,"uid":217416,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"戰機Foodpanda<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"台灣軍方一架F16戰機，昨晚在花蓮夜航訓練期間懷疑失事，軍方經過24小時搜救，未發現殘骸，只是指海面上有疑似油漬，仍待確認。<span class=\"red\">空軍司令熊厚基，晚上召開記者會，指雷達顯示，戰機在20秒內急墜7000呎，飛行員失聯前的無線電通話紀錄顯示，並未回報機械異常</span>，初步認為戰機機械故障可能性較低，戰機當時在爬升過程進入雲層轉彎，不排除飛行員產生錯覺，導致空間迷向出事。<br />\n蔡英文令停飛F-16戰機檢查<br />\n總統蔡英文表示，已停飛所有F-16戰機，並進行檢查，並要求空軍徹查事故原因，該負責就負責、該檢討就檢討，同時國防戰備任務不能鬆懈。<br />\n失聯軍機的機師是44歲的上校蔣正志，飛行總時數達到2230小時，F16飛行時數超過1800小時。當局至今出動11架次搜救機，和20艘次艦艇參與搜救工作，期間發射逾百顆照明彈，黑鷹直升機今早由花蓮出發，接替搜救任務。軍方指，四架F-16戰機昨日傍晚6時後由花蓮基地升空，其中一架2分鐘後與控制塔失去聯絡，另外三架戰機的飛行員未聽聞無線電呼叫。<br />\n解放軍3架軍機飛入台灣防空識別區<br />\n台灣空軍指，解放軍3架運8反潛機、干擾機及通信對抗機，今日飛入台灣西南防空識別區，空軍派遣空中兵力應對、廣播驅離，今次是解放軍軍機今個月第14度抵近台灣空域。<br />\n台灣戰機大半個月兩宗事故<br />\n上月底台灣一架F-5戰機在台東訓練期間墜海，飛行員傷重殉職；美國副國務卿克拉奇9月訪台後，解放軍軍機頻頻抵台灣空域飛行，台灣戰機不斷升空監控，令飛行員出現疲態。"},{"pid":"c9faf148b1b2bc19370eb923e135723d11d483b8","tid":2292491,"uid":330227,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n看圖說故事？"},{"pid":"b67acfc180f296dbcbcbb0b530412cd8e50d5478","tid":2292491,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收咗中共幾多錢　連人帶機帶去支那"},{"pid":"3eae81695bf661a4600774ef9a797d272fab7883","tid":2292491,"uid":210755,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c9faf148b1b2bc19370eb923e135723d11d483b8","tid":2292491,"uid":330227,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n看圖說故事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:23:17.000Z","msg":"係，廢老親戚話微信群瘋傳"},{"pid":"49f540ed09bdd0cf089c3bfc18f54783165201c3","tid":2292491,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3eae81695bf661a4600774ef9a797d272fab7883","tid":2292491,"uid":210755,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c9faf148b1b2bc19370eb923e135723d11d483b8","tid":2292491,"uid":330227,"like":13,"dislik